metadata.description:
My original character "Trami" as #megamiathome style!

"Trami" is an incarnation of a tiger.
 She informs you of the danger.
 She also brings good luck in the game.

This artwork complies with the MEGAMI art license.

With all my heartfelt gratitude for the MEGAMI project that gave us such a great opportunity.

2048 x 2048 pixel
